      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 14:44:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔债券因火灾缩短诺沃亚纽约之行而遭受打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/ecuador-fires-cut-noboa-s-new-york-trip-short-and-bonds-take-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔遭遇 60 多年来最严重的旱灾，导致森林火灾、全国停电，并迫使该国领导人缩短纽约之行。投资者现在担心他的支持率会受到影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/ecuador-fires-cut-noboa-s-new-york-trip-short-and-bonds-take-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 14:44:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉加德称欧洲央行在下次会议前增强了通胀信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/lagarde-says-ecb-is-getting-more-confident-of-taming-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，欧洲央行对于控制通胀越来越乐观，并将在10月份的利率决策中对此进行反思。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/lagarde-says-ecb-is-getting-more-confident-of-taming-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 13:11:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
